1
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:12,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:08,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:12,020 --> 00:01:15,140
[Episode 21]

5
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:18,140
I wanted to form a cultivation partnership with Lifei,

6
00:01:18,880 --> 00:01:20,170
but I feared that my uncle wouldn't agree.

7
00:01:22,470 --> 00:01:23,620
She panicked

8
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,220
and went straight in to ask why.

9
00:01:32,470 --> 00:01:34,620
Since both Lei Xiuyuan and Ji Tongzhou

10
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,500
want to vouch for Jiang Lifei,

11
00:01:37,470 --> 00:01:39,700
we can test whether these three

12
00:01:40,270 --> 00:01:41,810
are lying.

13
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:47,450
My disciple and Jiang Lifei were indeed with me.

14
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:53,780
Are you going to interrogate me as well?

15
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:08,500
Xiuyuan!

16
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:20,620
Sir, what is this?

17
00:02:20,830 --> 00:02:23,340
What have I done to offend you?

18
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,740
My eyes must have been playing tricks on me just now.

19
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:28,650
Maybe I was mistaken.

20
00:02:28,710 --> 00:02:29,340
Everyone,

21
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:30,740
we've found the culprit!

22
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:38,850
Mr. Shi!

23
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:40,570
Shi Chengtian,

24
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:42,060
tell everyone about your dealings

25
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,020
with the demons!

26
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,300
You're lying!

27
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,900
When did I ever collude with demons?

28
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,370
This monster-bewitching powder

29
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:54,370
was found on you.

30
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,530
Still denying it?

31
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,220
You...

32
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:57,650
Impossible!

33
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,410
I used up that powder long ago!

34
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,130
You're framing me!

35
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,340
This is a setup! A frame-up!

36
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:07,970
Everyone.

37
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,220
Mr. Shen.

38
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,060
Mr. Shen.

39
00:03:10,270 --> 00:03:10,810
Mr. Shen.

40
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,570
He's the one who colluded with demons.

41
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:14,090
It's got nothing to do with us.

42
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,740
We were just trying to make some money.

43
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,020
Right, right.

44
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,460
That person in red said

45
00:03:18,990 --> 00:03:20,090
that if we drove the beasts mad,

46
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,620
we could

47
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,460
kill them openly and sell them for money.

48
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,180
Person in red?

49
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,090
Yes, yes.

50
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,130
Someone!

51
00:03:33,550 --> 00:03:35,340
Take Shi Chengtian and that man away!

52
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,690
Keep them under tight watch!

53
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,340
Wait, I...

54
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,130
- It's got nothing to do with me.
- Shen...

55
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,690
It's nothing to do with me!

56
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:43,060
Mercy!

57
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,900
It's got nothing to do with me!

58
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,370
Have mercy!

59
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,810
That person in red Shi Chengtian mentioned

60
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:52,180
must be a demon Guardian.

61
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,620
It's Rakshasa.

62
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,900
I fought her last night.

63
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,650
So Rakshasa is behind all this.

64
00:04:00,990 --> 00:04:02,340
Demons are cunning and treacherous.

65
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,460
Hard to guard against.

66
00:04:04,270 --> 00:04:05,900
From now on, we need to be extra careful

67
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:08,530
and watch out for demons sneaking in.

68
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,690
Given Shi Chengtian's strength,

69
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:14,970
he couldn't have helped a demon escape the city.

70
00:04:16,590 --> 00:04:18,090
We still need to find out

71
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:20,010
who the real inside contact is.

72
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,660
After last night's city-wide sweep,

73
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:25,810
the demons wouldn't dare stay.

74
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:26,940
They've probably fled by now.

75
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,540
Facing such a massive threat,

76
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,890
we must stand together.

77
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:33,770
That was the whole point of this Shanhai Gathering.

78
00:04:34,470 --> 00:04:35,690
Elder Cuixuan! This is bad!

79
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,300
Sir,

80
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:43,100
Wuyue Court just sent an urgent message.

81
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:45,540
A demon spy broke into Hushe Peak.

82
00:04:55,710 --> 00:04:56,450
Sir,

83
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:59,330
does Wuyue Court have a Hushe Peak?

84
00:04:59,790 --> 00:05:00,420
Quiet.

85
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,860
No more questions.

86
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,940
All Wuyue Court disciples,

87
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:13,330
return with me immediately.

88
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:14,450
Sir,

89
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,690
Jiang Lifei and Lei Xiuyuan

90
00:05:16,710 --> 00:05:18,100
were my friends at the academy.

91
00:05:18,470 --> 00:05:19,690
I'd like them to stay a few more days

92
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:20,940
so I can ask how things are going there.

93
00:05:25,790 --> 00:05:26,450
Cuixuan.

94
00:05:31,710 --> 00:05:33,300
Duanming City has just settled down.

95
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:36,330
We could use skilled disciples to help with defense.

96
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,100
Do me a favor

97
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:40,980
and let them stay a little longer.

98
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,130
Fine.

99
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,180
You two stay and help.

100
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:50,370
Once Duanming City is secure,

101
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:52,180
come back right away.

102
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,640
[Duanming City Inn]

103
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,370
Are these demons everywhere at once?

104
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,210
Causing trouble here while ambushing us there.

105
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,740
But Deng and I had a deal.

106
00:06:19,030 --> 00:06:19,770
If anything goes wrong,

107
00:06:19,790 --> 00:06:20,570
he'd come in right away.

108
00:06:21,030 --> 00:06:21,660
How is it?

109
00:06:22,150 --> 00:06:22,940
Not bad, right?

110
00:06:27,350 --> 00:06:28,570
Will they suspect something?

111
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:29,980
Relax.

112
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,130
I've cleared it with my master.

113
00:06:31,150 --> 00:06:32,100
He'll play along.

114
00:06:34,790 --> 00:06:37,770
Sorry to drag everyone into this.

115
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,420
What are you talking about?

116
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:41,420
This is something we want to do too.

117
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,420
Gelin's right.

118
00:06:44,150 --> 00:06:46,330
We were born into the imperial bloodline

119
00:06:46,790 --> 00:06:48,300
and have been hunted by Longming Sanctuary.

120
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:50,660
If it weren't for righteous people risking their lives to save us,

121
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,300
we wouldn't be here today.

122
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:55,450
Now that

123
00:06:55,470 --> 00:06:56,980
we're seeing such injustice,

124
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,690
how could we stand by?

125
00:07:00,590 --> 00:07:02,300
We worked well together

126
00:07:02,350 --> 00:07:03,130
and got out clean.

127
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:08,100
I always thought Mr. Zuo Qiu's talk

128
00:07:08,790 --> 00:07:10,100
about serving the people

129
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,100
and purifying the world

130
00:07:12,790 --> 00:07:14,660
was just empty words.

131
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,620
Now I see

132
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,810
how hard it is to stand up to power

133
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,860
and fight for what's right.

134
00:07:21,470 --> 00:07:22,890
Hard as it was, we did it.

135
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:24,500
Come on!

136
00:07:24,910 --> 00:07:25,810
Everyone,

137
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,300
we've triumphed.

138
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,420
Time for a good drink.

139
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:29,890
- Here. - Cheers!

140
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,210
What a shame.

141
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:40,690
Here.

142
00:07:40,710 --> 00:07:42,660
These sects are divided.

143
00:07:43,710 --> 00:07:44,980
With a little provocation from the demons,

144
00:07:45,230 --> 00:07:46,810
we fall apart

145
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:47,690
and turn on each other.

146
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,130
News reached my master, Sect Leader Miao.

147
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:52,620
He told Changyue and me to hurry back to Dizang Sect.

148
00:07:55,790 --> 00:07:57,740
My uncle wants me back at Xingzheng Hall as soon as possible.

149
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,180
The demons sent only a single Guardian,

150
00:08:00,710 --> 00:08:02,500
yet they threw Mountain and Sea Sects into utter chaos.

151
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,300
We can't underestimate them.

152
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,010
He wants me back to train

153
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,330
so I'll be ready

154
00:08:07,350 --> 00:08:08,500
for the Sea Calamity.

155
00:08:10,590 --> 00:08:12,100
We barely had time to catch up,

156
00:08:12,470 --> 00:08:13,540
and now you're all leaving.

157
00:08:14,230 --> 00:08:15,250
Who knows

158
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,770
when we'll see each other again?

159
00:08:20,590 --> 00:08:22,420
We'll cross that bridge when we get to it.

160
00:08:22,710 --> 00:08:23,620
Next time we meet,

161
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:25,420
it'll likely be the Sea Calamity.

162
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,810
Before that,

163
00:08:38,230 --> 00:08:40,420
I'd like to ask you all for a favor.

164
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:50,060
Ever since I was little, I've known a girl.

165
00:08:51,710 --> 00:08:54,940
I think she's the most beautiful

166
00:08:55,710 --> 00:08:56,730
and lovely girl in the world.

167
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:01,140
I've always wanted to marry her.

168
00:09:03,470 --> 00:09:05,300
We all know.

169
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,210
You all are the dearest friends to Changyue and me.

170
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,660
Before we part,

171
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,970
I want you all to witness this.

172
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:25,140
Ye,

173
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,060
- you... - Changyue.

174
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:28,780
The Sea Calamity is coming.

175
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:30,780
No one knows what lies ahead.

176
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,330
Better to cherish the one beside you

177
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:35,660
than to live with regret.

178
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:39,730
Changyue,

179
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,940
will you be my wife?

180
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,210
My head hurts.

181
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,330
I'm going to my room to rest.

182
00:10:02,590 --> 00:10:03,210
Changyue.

183
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:07,610
Changyue.

184
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:15,610
I'll go check.

185
00:10:37,630 --> 00:10:38,210
Tongzhou.

186
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:40,140
During the Wanxian Sect's questioning today,

187
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,210
you were quick on your feet.

188
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,610
You're getting almost as good at lying as I am.

189
00:10:47,460 --> 00:10:48,300
Actually,

190
00:10:49,590 --> 00:10:50,780
I wasn't entirely lying.

191
00:10:57,230 --> 00:10:57,850
Tongzhou,

192
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,730
we made that three-year pact back at Lugong Town.

193
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:02,140
How about we move it up?

194
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:05,330
Sure.

195
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:07,060
We should've done this long ago.

196
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:10,020
But I won't lose.

197
00:11:11,470 --> 00:11:11,940
Tomorrow?

198
00:11:12,820 --> 00:11:13,380
At the Wu hour.

199
00:11:13,990 --> 00:11:14,850
Alright. Enough.

200
00:11:16,460 --> 00:11:17,210
Why fight?

201
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:18,780
Aren't you tired?

202
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:21,260
Right now, the most important thing

203
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:22,780
is helping Ye Ye and Changyue

204
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,090
with their wedding.

205
00:11:24,470 --> 00:11:25,450
If you really need to fight,

206
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:26,660
wait until it's over

207
00:11:27,100 --> 00:11:28,020
and find a place to settle it.

208
00:11:29,110 --> 00:11:29,690
- Alright. - Fine.

209
00:11:38,420 --> 00:11:39,690
After Fanghu Island,

210
00:11:40,820 --> 00:11:41,780
I suddenly realized

211
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:44,210
I can't wait any longer.

212
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:45,810
Waiting any longer

213
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:48,660
would only hurt you and Gelin.

214
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:51,450
Time slips away

215
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:53,810
in the blink of an eye.

216
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:56,380
I don't want to waste any more time.

217
00:11:59,230 --> 00:12:00,380
I want to be with you.

218
00:12:02,980 --> 00:12:04,540
I want you to be my wife.

219
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:05,540
- I want... - Enough, Ye!

220
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:06,970
Stop.

221
00:12:07,830 --> 00:12:09,300
I said I needed time to think.

222
00:12:29,660 --> 00:12:30,210
Gelin.

223
00:12:31,590 --> 00:12:32,260
Changyue.

224
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,810
You should be discussing the wedding with Ye.

225
00:12:37,830 --> 00:12:38,570
Why are you looking for me?

226
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:39,610
Gelin.

227
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:41,330
Ye and I... I...

228
00:12:41,470 --> 00:12:42,180
Changyue.

229
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,140
You seem smart,

230
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:49,090
but you're really clueless.

231
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,780
I used to worry

232
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:53,020
Ye wouldn't take good care of you.

233
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:55,900
Turns out I worried for nothing.

234
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,020
He takes great care of you.

235
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:01,730
He's worth marrying.

236
00:13:08,230 --> 00:13:08,900
Gelin.

237
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:10,940
I let you down.

238
00:13:11,540 --> 00:13:14,540
Before, I was too caught up in my own things.

239
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:16,380
I thought you were still young,

240
00:13:16,590 --> 00:13:18,260
so I kept things from you.

241
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,180
You ended up going all the way to the East Sea

242
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,450
and suffering so much.

243
00:13:23,510 --> 00:13:24,780
It's all my fault.

244
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:28,180
I'm sorry.

245
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,020
Changyue,

246
00:13:31,660 --> 00:13:32,730
don't worry.

247
00:13:33,710 --> 00:13:35,450
I don't like Ye anymore.

248
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:37,060
Really.

249
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:41,660
I like someone else now.

250
00:13:42,540 --> 00:13:44,090
I don't even remember those childhood things.

251
00:13:47,830 --> 00:13:48,420
Gelin.

252
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:50,780
Listen to me,

253
00:13:51,230 --> 00:13:53,570
liking someone isn't a crime.

254
00:13:53,590 --> 00:13:55,330
You didn't have to run so far away.

255
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:57,140
I really don't like him anymore.

256
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:59,020
You don't have to turn him down because of me.

257
00:14:01,660 --> 00:14:02,810
Ye was right.

258
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,180
Time slips away

259
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:06,420
in the blink of an eye.

260
00:14:08,110 --> 00:14:09,450
We shouldn't waste any more time.

261
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:14,090
I genuinely wish you two the best.

262
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,090
Unless...

263
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:20,330
Unless, after you get married,

264
00:14:20,590 --> 00:14:21,850
you decide you don't want me anymore.

265
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:29,780
What are you saying, silly girl?

266
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:32,180
Talking nonsense.

267
00:14:34,630 --> 00:14:35,970
Always talking nonsense.

268
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:42,540
No matter where we are

269
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,450
or how far apart,

270
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:46,690
I'll always miss you.

271
00:14:47,350 --> 00:14:50,180
And I believe you'll miss me too.

272
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:52,810
We'll always be sisters,

273
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:55,540
through life and death.

274
00:15:34,110 --> 00:15:34,690
Gelin.

275
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:36,330
What's wrong?

276
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:41,490
Lifei said you went to Yingcui Island.

277
00:15:41,990 --> 00:15:44,090
I thought I'd never see you again.

278
00:15:49,590 --> 00:15:50,940
I thought you were all leaving

279
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:52,180
and never coming back.

280
00:15:53,470 --> 00:15:54,300
I didn't want you...

281
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:57,300
you all to worry.

282
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,300
You're hurt?

283
00:16:14,710 --> 00:16:15,380
Feeling better?

284
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:28,810
Treasure it that much?

285
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:34,970
Did some special girl give it to you?

286
00:16:37,110 --> 00:16:38,850
It's the crest of the Jiufeng Clan.

287
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,570
Why no eyes?

288
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,450
Did you lose them?

289
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:56,780
You want to see the eyes?

290
00:16:57,990 --> 00:16:58,690
Yeah.

291
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,570
It would look better

292
00:17:00,710 --> 00:17:01,690
with eyes.

293
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:38,580
This is...?

294
00:17:56,990 --> 00:17:57,730
Now it has one.

295
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:07,340
What did you do?

296
00:18:14,340 --> 00:18:16,050
I swear by the Jiufeng Clan,

297
00:18:16,990 --> 00:18:18,730
I will never betray Baili Gelin.

298
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:23,690
Through life and death,

299
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,180
we'll never part.

300
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:29,940
Lu,

301
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,730
are you crazy?

302
00:18:36,470 --> 00:18:37,900
Take it off for me.

303
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:40,490
Once it's on, it can never be removed.

304
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:42,490
Baili Gelin,

305
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,730
you started this.

306
00:19:14,550 --> 00:19:15,210
Come out.

307
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:20,380
My Lord,

308
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:24,340
have you finally seen their true colors now?

309
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,730
Stop using the demon clan.

310
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:28,900
Their situation

311
00:19:29,840 --> 00:19:31,180
is no different from yours 500 years ago.

312
00:19:32,510 --> 00:19:33,770
My Lord, you remember me now?

313
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:36,210
Your soul has been hiding in a bone-devouring butterfly.

314
00:19:37,230 --> 00:19:38,250
You've waited centuries

315
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:40,450
for a result, haven't you?

316
00:19:41,470 --> 00:19:42,210
The Sea Calamity is coming.

317
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:44,210
Instead of mutual destruction,

318
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:45,970
it's better to go home while you can.

319
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:48,490
My Lord!

320
00:19:57,710 --> 00:19:58,380
Xiuyuan,

321
00:19:58,510 --> 00:19:59,340
thank you

322
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:00,340
for helping with the wedding.

323
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:03,210
I only hope that one day,

324
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:05,900
you can step out of being a stand-in.

325
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,620
But I still have a mission to fulfill.

326
00:20:08,470 --> 00:20:09,970
Until it's done,

327
00:20:10,840 --> 00:20:11,940
I can't afford a single wrong step.

328
00:20:13,640 --> 00:20:14,450
Mission?

329
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:17,010
The true king of Gaolu

330
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:18,490
isn't named Ye,

331
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:19,860
but

332
00:20:21,310 --> 00:20:22,010
Yecha.

333
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:26,420
That Demon Lord?

334
00:20:27,030 --> 00:20:27,970
In ancient times,

335
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:30,210
when Yecha was still a Divine Lord,

336
00:20:30,840 --> 00:20:32,970
our ancestors followed him.

337
00:20:33,510 --> 00:20:34,420
A thousand years ago,

338
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:35,450
heaven's wrath descended.

339
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:38,860
The Ye clan was ordered to guard the Central Plains.

340
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,210
Our duty is to find the Divine Lord

341
00:20:40,310 --> 00:20:41,660
and end heaven's wrath.

342
00:20:42,070 --> 00:20:43,290
That is our mission.

343
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:44,530
So

344
00:20:45,270 --> 00:20:46,770
until it's fulfilled,

345
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,180
I don't even dare to die.

346
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:50,820
Is the mission

347
00:20:53,230 --> 00:20:54,340
really that important?

348
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:55,860
A true promise is etched in stone.

349
00:20:56,310 --> 00:20:57,380
It can't be broken lightly.

350
00:20:58,270 --> 00:20:59,660
Not in a thousand years,

351
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:01,380
not in ten thousand.

352
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:04,940
Oh,

353
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,380
I saw

354
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:08,180
you and Lifei made up again.

355
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:09,050
So,

356
00:21:09,340 --> 00:21:11,100
are you two in love?

357
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:12,620
I do like her.

358
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:15,420
But I don't know how she feels.

359
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:18,530
Lifei seems happy enough.

360
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:19,730
It's probably mutual.

361
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:26,690
Uncle.

362
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,450
I'd like to stay for Ye Ye's wedding

363
00:21:30,990 --> 00:21:31,900
before returning to Xingzheng Hall.

364
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:37,380
Our highest techniques require cutting off attachments and desires.

365
00:21:39,270 --> 00:21:42,100
If you don't focus on your training,

366
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:44,380
how will you help your brother

367
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:45,820
secure the kingdom

368
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:46,970
and achieve greatness?

369
00:21:47,550 --> 00:21:48,290
Do I have to give up

370
00:21:48,310 --> 00:21:49,730
the one I love to achieve greatness?

371
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:51,420
Remember who you are.

372
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:53,290
Can't a prince of the Yue State

373
00:21:53,310 --> 00:21:54,420
pursue the one he loves?

374
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:56,690
To protect this kingdom,

375
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,580
you must master the Xuanhua Sacred Fire

376
00:21:58,640 --> 00:21:59,620
and attain immortality!

377
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:01,140
I don't need the Xuanhua Sacred Fire

378
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:01,940
or immortality

379
00:22:02,230 --> 00:22:03,250
to protect the Yue State!

380
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:06,100
Jiang Lifei's heart already belongs to another.

381
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:07,940
Can't you see that?

382
00:22:10,990 --> 00:22:12,290
Lifei has feelings for me.

383
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:16,770
At worst, I'll give up my title as Prince

384
00:22:17,030 --> 00:22:18,050
and abandon my path to immortality!

385
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:19,140
You!

386
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:20,180
You...

387
00:22:36,510 --> 00:22:37,140
Changyue,

388
00:22:37,750 --> 00:22:40,290
no bride in the world is more beautiful than you.

389
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:43,290
It's just this dress that's beautiful.

390
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:45,290
Jiao prepared it.

391
00:22:46,470 --> 00:22:47,730
She said

392
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:50,490
she'd give Lifei one when she gets married.

393
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:36,900
So beautiful.

394
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:50,380
From the primal chaos,

395
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:51,770
yin and yang were formed.

396
00:23:52,640 --> 00:23:53,970
Love between mortals

397
00:23:54,070 --> 00:23:55,530
is passed down through rites and teachings.

398
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:57,580
Today, bound by ritual,

399
00:23:57,790 --> 00:23:58,970
they wed before these guests.

400
00:23:59,840 --> 00:24:01,100
They share the ritual feast

401
00:24:01,100 --> 00:24:02,380
and drink the nuptial wine.

402
00:24:02,710 --> 00:24:03,770
With heaven and earth as witness,

403
00:24:04,160 --> 00:24:05,690
under the sun and the moon.

404
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,730
First bow to heaven and earth.

405
00:24:13,990 --> 00:24:14,660
Tongzhou!

406
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:15,900
Tongzhou.

407
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:18,380
Lanya?

408
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:20,380
Lanya.

409
00:24:20,550 --> 00:24:21,180
Tongzhou.

410
00:24:23,070 --> 00:24:23,690
Lanya,

411
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:25,250
what happened?

412
00:24:25,600 --> 00:24:26,290
Tongzhou.

413
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:27,860
Wugou invaded the Yue State!

414
00:24:28,100 --> 00:24:29,140
Duantu has fallen!

415
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:33,100
- What? - What?

416
00:24:37,840 --> 00:24:38,660
Tonghe...

417
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,970
Tonghe was captured by Zong Quan!

418
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:42,620
What?

419
00:24:45,230 --> 00:24:46,180
It was Zhijie.

420
00:24:46,990 --> 00:24:48,730
He held off Longming Sanctuary

421
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:50,450
so I could escape.

422
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:52,250
We're going back to Duantu right now!

423
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:53,490
Don't act rashly.

424
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,340
Since Zong Quan showed up,

425
00:24:56,790 --> 00:24:59,250
Longming Sanctuary must have fully mobilized.

426
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:02,450
Let's return to Xingzheng Hall, gather the disciples,

427
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,100
and go rescue him together.

428
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:05,530
Tongzhou!

429
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:13,450
Are you ready?

430
00:25:18,750 --> 00:25:20,050
If you are, let's move.

431
00:25:20,230 --> 00:25:21,340
The three of us will go to Duantu with you.

432
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:23,290
Ye Ye and Changyue are going back to Dizang Sect first,

433
00:25:23,470 --> 00:25:24,530
then they'll meet up with us.

434
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:25,690
Right.

435
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,730
Longming Sanctuary is acting against all reason.

436
00:25:28,230 --> 00:25:29,730
We'll report to our sect leader

437
00:25:30,070 --> 00:25:31,050
and join forces with other sects

438
00:25:31,070 --> 00:25:32,290
to stop them.

439
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:33,620
The situation is unclear.

440
00:25:34,270 --> 00:25:35,290
You'll all be dragged into this.

441
00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:36,860
If we can't

442
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,770
watch out for each other in times like these,

443
00:25:39,070 --> 00:25:40,620
what's the point of cultivation?

444
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:42,660
- Right. - Yes.

445
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:11,380
How could this happen?

446
00:26:26,070 --> 00:26:26,690
Mo Chen.

447
00:26:41,710 --> 00:26:42,290
Chen!

448
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:43,530
Chen.

449
00:26:44,100 --> 00:26:44,690
Chen.

450
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:46,290
Tongzhou.

451
00:26:46,750 --> 00:26:48,420
It was Longming Sanctuary.

452
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,900
It was Zong Quan.

453
00:27:17,070 --> 00:27:18,250
Move! Behave!

454
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:19,250
- Go! - Keep up!

455
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,420
Hurry!

456
00:27:20,420 --> 00:27:21,420
[Xingzheng Hall]

457
00:27:23,340 --> 00:27:27,210
You must avenge

458
00:27:28,710 --> 00:27:29,730
us.

459
00:27:30,030 --> 00:27:30,690
Chen.

460
00:27:31,230 --> 00:27:31,860
Chen!

461
00:27:33,470 --> 00:27:34,140
Chen!

462
00:28:06,790 --> 00:28:08,180
No survivors.

463
00:28:09,270 --> 00:28:10,660
It's been less than two years

464
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:11,730
since we heavily wounded Zong Quan.

465
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:14,210
How did his cultivation recover so fast?

466
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,530
Not just recovered.

467
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:19,420
He seems even stronger.

468
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:30,530
He wiped out

469
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:33,250
the entire Xingzheng Hall in a single night.

470
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:36,530
What kind of evil art has he been practicing?

471
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,860
Is it the Spirit-Devouring Canon?

472
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:45,820
After Gaolu fell,

473
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:47,450
Longming Sanctuary used every means

474
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,620
to hunt down the imperial bloodline.

475
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,620
They'll use the same tricks again.

476
00:28:57,800 --> 00:29:00,360
[Yue State Imperial Palace]

477
00:29:04,470 --> 00:29:05,100
Tonghe.

478
00:29:05,360 --> 00:29:06,180
Are you alright?

479
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:31,290
Tonghe.

480
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:32,250
No.

481
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:33,660
No.

482
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:36,970
Tonghe!

483
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:38,770
No.

484
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:40,420
Don't leave me.

485
00:29:47,070 --> 00:29:49,380
Tonghe. Tonghe!

486
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:52,420
Tonghe.

487
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,340
No!

488
00:30:02,030 --> 00:30:04,730
What a touching display of brotherly love.

489
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:14,450
Prince Ying conspired with Xingzheng Hall to usurp the throne.

490
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:16,010
The Emperor of Yue is dead.

491
00:30:16,710 --> 00:30:19,770
How do you like my gift?

492
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:21,660
Zong Quan.

493
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:24,620
I'll kill you!

494
00:30:32,270 --> 00:30:34,180
Xuanhua Sacred Fire?

495
00:30:42,600 --> 00:30:43,450
What a pity.

496
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,900
You haven't even mastered it.

497
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:47,140
You've only reached the second level.

498
00:30:47,230 --> 00:30:48,010
Otherwise,

499
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:50,100
you might have traded a few strikes with me.

500
00:30:50,710 --> 00:30:52,010
You practice evil arts?

501
00:30:59,600 --> 00:31:00,820
The law of this world is simple.

502
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,290
The strong rule.

503
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:04,770
As long as you have the power to control everything,

504
00:31:05,070 --> 00:31:07,050
the means don't matter!

505
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:07,900
But

506
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:11,690
I don't want to kill you yet.

507
00:31:16,230 --> 00:31:17,820
Your spirit power is pure,

508
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:19,340
and your constitution is excellent.

509
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:22,210
You'll be useful to me.

510
00:31:33,990 --> 00:31:34,660
Tongzhou.

511
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:37,450
Get Tongzhou out of here!

512
00:31:38,030 --> 00:31:38,620
Let's go.

513
00:31:57,710 --> 00:31:58,690
Zhao Zhijie, are you insane?

514
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:00,620
Zhao Zhijie?

515
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,100
They've all been controlled.

516
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:38,290
Xuanhua Sacred Fire.

517
00:32:39,470 --> 00:32:40,820
Demon Annihilation!

518
00:33:02,470 --> 00:33:03,100
Lanya?

519
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:15,820
Mr. Xuanshan!

520
00:33:16,470 --> 00:33:17,100
Tongzhou!

521
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,380
Mr. Xuanshan.

522
00:33:18,840 --> 00:33:19,380
Mr. Xuanshan.

523
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:20,250
Are you alright?

524
00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:55,010
Mr. Xuanshan.

525
00:33:55,550 --> 00:33:56,580
Mr. Xuanshan. Mr. Xuanshan!

526
00:33:56,990 --> 00:33:58,180
Mr. Xuanshan, hang in there.

527
00:33:58,310 --> 00:33:58,900
Mr. Xuanshan.

528
00:33:59,400 --> 00:33:59,970
Remember,

529
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:04,620
this is the fourth level of the Xuanhua Sacred Fire.

530
00:34:05,790 --> 00:34:07,100
Incineration!

531
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:07,770
Mr. Xuanshan.

532
00:34:08,160 --> 00:34:09,340
Mr. Xuanshan!

533
00:34:12,710 --> 00:34:14,880
[Duantu City]

534
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:24,450
Let me go.

535
00:34:25,030 --> 00:34:25,570
Let go!

536
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:27,380
A Xingzheng Hall disciple!

537
00:34:27,510 --> 00:34:28,090
Perfect.

538
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:30,010
Xu will reward us well.

539
00:34:30,470 --> 00:34:32,700
Hold him tight. Don't let him move.

540
00:35:09,860 --> 00:35:10,490
Lu.

541
00:35:17,110 --> 00:35:18,650
What's this thing for?

542
00:35:19,240 --> 00:35:20,570
It's Longming Sanctuary's puppet seal.

543
00:35:21,420 --> 00:35:21,820
Well...

544
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:22,820
Pup...

545
00:35:22,940 --> 00:35:23,780
Can it be removed?

546
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:26,220
Yes, by pulling the puppet spider out.

547
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:27,450
But

548
00:35:28,300 --> 00:35:29,340
one wrong move

549
00:35:29,670 --> 00:35:30,650
and it will backfire,

550
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:32,220
snapping the host's neck.

551
00:35:38,590 --> 00:35:39,170
Mingli,

552
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:41,130
after you got hurt on Fanghu Island,

553
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:42,610
didn't you go back to Xingzheng Hall early?

554
00:35:42,780 --> 00:35:44,170
How did they catch you in Duantu?

555
00:35:44,670 --> 00:35:46,300
When I returned from the East Sea,

556
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:49,260
I found Longming Sanctuary had ambushed Xingzheng Hall.

557
00:35:53,780 --> 00:35:54,420
Behave!

558
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:55,860
Move it! Hurry!

559
00:35:55,900 --> 00:35:57,700
- Move! - Hurry!

560
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:59,010
I went to find my brother for help,

561
00:35:59,470 --> 00:36:00,490
but his house was empty.

562
00:36:00,990 --> 00:36:02,220
When I went to the Commandery Princess's Manor for news,

563
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:03,940
I ran right into Longming Sanctuary's people.

564
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:06,970
Now their spies are everywhere.

565
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,420
Still have no word from my brother.

566
00:36:10,070 --> 00:36:10,820
What about Prince Ying?

567
00:36:11,550 --> 00:36:12,450
Is he with you?

568
00:36:31,720 --> 00:36:32,260
Uncle.

569
00:36:32,980 --> 00:36:33,530
Uncle.

570
00:36:36,030 --> 00:36:36,650
Uncle.

571
00:36:58,460 --> 00:36:59,300
He'll pull through.

572
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,220
Uncle

573
00:37:09,720 --> 00:37:10,490
Tongzhou,

574
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:13,820
I pushed you into the fire today.

575
00:37:14,470 --> 00:37:16,970
Will you hold it against me someday?

576
00:37:19,340 --> 00:37:20,090
No.

577
00:37:21,300 --> 00:37:21,820
Uncle.

578
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:24,300
I won't defy you anymore.

579
00:37:25,550 --> 00:37:26,490
I'll listen to you.

580
00:37:27,470 --> 00:37:28,490
I'll cut off attachments

581
00:37:29,340 --> 00:37:30,300
and master the Sacred Fire.

582
00:37:32,030 --> 00:37:32,610
Uncle.

583
00:37:33,780 --> 00:37:34,700
Don't leave me.

584
00:37:35,420 --> 00:37:35,940
Uncle.

585
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:37,780
You must live.

586
00:37:39,150 --> 00:37:42,740
Live on for all eternity, in the name of the Yue State.

587
00:37:44,670 --> 00:37:45,260
Uncle.

588
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:47,130
Uncle.

589
00:37:48,720 --> 00:37:49,450
Uncle!

590
00:38:00,110 --> 00:38:02,450
If you ever feel wronged or unhappy out there,

591
00:38:02,900 --> 00:38:04,050
come back to me.

592
00:38:04,550 --> 00:38:05,820
Forget cultivation if it comes to that.

593
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:07,010
I'll support you.

594
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:10,170
Got it.

595
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:11,490
I'm going.

596
00:38:28,780 --> 00:38:29,340
Tonghe.

597
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:31,130
Tonghe.

598
00:38:35,670 --> 00:38:36,260
Tonghe.

599
00:38:40,110 --> 00:38:40,700
Tonghe.

600
00:38:54,990 --> 00:38:55,570
Tonghe!

601
00:38:58,030 --> 00:38:58,570
Tonghe.

602
00:38:58,990 --> 00:38:59,610
Tonghe.

603
00:39:00,190 --> 00:39:00,820
Tonghe?

604
00:39:01,420 --> 00:39:02,010
Tonghe!

605
00:39:08,110 --> 00:39:08,860
Tongzhou.

606
00:39:10,150 --> 00:39:13,050
The Yue State and Jingwu

607
00:39:18,550 --> 00:39:19,820
are yours now.

608
00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:21,450
No, Tonghe.

609
00:39:22,340 --> 00:39:22,780
No.

610
00:39:23,030 --> 00:39:23,570
Tonghe.

611
00:39:23,780 --> 00:39:24,380
Tonghe.

612
00:39:25,590 --> 00:39:26,090
No!

613
00:39:27,030 --> 00:39:27,780
Tonghe!

614
00:39:30,340 --> 00:39:31,090
Tongzhou.

615
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:32,820
Lifei?

616
00:39:33,510 --> 00:39:34,130
Lifei!

617
00:39:35,340 --> 00:39:35,970
Lifei.

618
00:39:36,550 --> 00:39:37,220
Lifei.

619
00:39:37,590 --> 00:39:38,450
Don't be scared.

620
00:39:38,590 --> 00:39:39,420
Be careful.

621
00:39:39,990 --> 00:39:41,650
You're still hurt. Don't get too worked up.

622
00:39:47,940 --> 00:39:49,780
You've been unconscious for five days.

623
00:39:50,110 --> 00:39:51,220
We were all so worried.

624
00:39:51,990 --> 00:39:52,860
Five days?

625
00:40:12,150 --> 00:40:12,970
All this time,

626
00:40:14,030 --> 00:40:15,610
you've been channeling your own spirit power

627
00:40:16,590 --> 00:40:17,450
into me?

628
00:40:21,300 --> 00:40:22,490
It was Gelin and Xiuyuan.

629
00:40:23,470 --> 00:40:24,900
They've been working day and night,

630
00:40:24,940 --> 00:40:26,220
setting up formations to repair your spirit meridians.

631
00:40:28,030 --> 00:40:29,220
Everything happened so fast.

632
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,940
So much at once.

633
00:40:32,670 --> 00:40:33,860
I couldn't even bring myself to come see you.

634
00:40:35,820 --> 00:40:36,490
Scared?

635
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:41,010
When we first escaped,

636
00:40:41,240 --> 00:40:43,340
your meridians were shattered. You were barely clinging to life.

637
00:40:44,590 --> 00:40:46,970
Thankfully, Xiuyuan kept us all grounded.

638
00:40:48,190 --> 00:40:49,300
Since the Shanhai Gathering,

639
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:51,340
seeing so many people and spirits die,

640
00:40:51,990 --> 00:40:53,170
I suddenly realized

641
00:40:54,550 --> 00:40:57,780
even the strongest lives are so fragile.

642
00:40:59,030 --> 00:41:00,490
I was afraid we couldn't save you.

643
00:41:00,820 --> 00:41:02,610
Afraid you'd give up and follow your family.

644
00:41:03,860 --> 00:41:04,420
So,

645
00:41:06,380 --> 00:41:07,530
I hid outside for days,

646
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:08,740
too scared to come in.

647
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:10,740
Until Xiuyuan said

648
00:41:11,110 --> 00:41:12,050
you'd live.

649
00:41:23,980 --> 00:41:25,220
What does it matter if I die?

650
00:41:28,240 --> 00:41:30,490
I'd rather it had been me.

651
00:41:32,460 --> 00:41:33,650
I'm so useless.

652
00:41:34,720 --> 00:41:36,090
I couldn't protect anyone.

653
00:41:39,670 --> 00:41:41,610
Why wasn't it me?

654
00:41:43,820 --> 00:41:45,650
Why am I the only one left?

655
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:49,050
Why only me?

656
00:41:49,900 --> 00:41:51,740
Because there is someone who need you.

657
00:42:03,980 --> 00:42:04,650
Xiuyuan.

658
00:42:15,110 --> 00:42:15,650
Tongzhou.

659
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:18,300
You don't have time to grieve.

660
00:42:19,070 --> 00:42:20,260
Your brother was a great emperor.

661
00:42:21,340 --> 00:42:22,340
Before Duantu fell,

662
00:42:23,340 --> 00:42:25,380
he managed to evacuate most of the people.

663
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:27,650
But many soldiers were captured

664
00:42:28,420 --> 00:42:29,170
and will be slaughtered.

665
00:42:30,150 --> 00:42:31,220
They are your people.

666
00:42:32,190 --> 00:42:33,170
You have to shoulder the responsibility.

667
00:42:35,860 --> 00:42:36,780
You don't have the right to give up.

668
00:42:37,820 --> 00:42:38,740
And you can't throw your life away.

669
00:42:42,050 --> 00:42:42,780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

670
00:42:42,780 --> 00:42:44,560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

671
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:59,480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

672
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:02,480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

673
00:43:02,560 --> 00:43:05,800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

674
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:09,080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

675
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:13,080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

676
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:16,560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

677
00:43:16,720 --> 00:43:22,800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

678
00:43:23,080 --> 00:43:27,200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

679
00:43:27,480 --> 00:43:30,160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

680
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:32,280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

681
00:43:32,400 --> 00:43:36,720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

682
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:40,720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

683
00:43:41,080 --> 00:43:44,080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

684
00:43:44,160 --> 00:43:50,280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

685
00:43:50,480 --> 00:43:54,200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

686
00:44:07,440 --> 00:44:11,200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

687
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:14,200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

688
00:44:14,280 --> 00:44:17,680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

689
00:44:17,680 --> 00:44:21,000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

690
00:44:21,160 --> 00:44:25,000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

691
00:44:25,160 --> 00:44:28,360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

692
00:44:28,600 --> 00:44:34,440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

693
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:38,920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

694
00:44:39,200 --> 00:44:41,960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

695
00:44:42,160 --> 00:44:44,000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

696
00:44:44,160 --> 00:44:48,360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

697
00:44:48,600 --> 00:44:52,480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

698
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:55,760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

699
00:44:55,960 --> 00:45:02,680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

700
00:45:02,720 --> 00:45:06,680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

701
00:45:06,920 --> 00:45:09,680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

702
00:45:09,800 --> 00:45:11,720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

703
00:45:11,880 --> 00:45:16,160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

704
00:45:16,360 --> 00:45:20,200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

705
00:45:20,440 --> 00:45:23,560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

706
00:45:23,600 --> 00:45:29,600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

707
00:45:30,000 --> 00:45:34,360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

